course_title: FOUNDATIONS OF LANGUAGE AND READING INSTRUCTION IN ELEMENTARY EDUCATION
description: Provides information and instructional strategies to support literacy learning. Addresses a wide range of literacy abilities including reading, writing, comprehending, and decoding. Focuses on the continuing developmental processes associated with becoming competent readers and writers.
